---
title: Indonesian Style Veg Satay Curry with Roasted Sweet Potato and Rice
description: Our Indonesian Style Veg Satay Curry is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W13_UK_V19432-3_Main_low-f1d8cd12.jpg
